#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "The VI Input Mode"
msgstr "Vnosni način VI"

#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "VI Input Mode"
msgstr "VI Vnosni način"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The goal of the VI mode is not to be a complete replacement for Vim and "
"support all Vim’s features. Its aim is to make the <quote>Vim way</quote> of "
"text editing - and the Vim habits learned - available for programs using the "
"&kappname; text editor as their internal editor."
msgstr ""
"Cilj načina VI ni popolna zamenjava za Vim in podpiranje vseh funkcij Vima. "
"Njegov cilj je omogočiti <quote>Vimov način</quote> urejanja besedila – in "
"pridobljene navade Vim – za programe, ki uporabljajo &kappname; urejevalnik "
"besedil kot njihov notranji urejevalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The VI mode aims to integrate nicely with the program and deviate from Vim’s "
"behavior where it makes sense. For example, <userinput><command>:w</"
"command></userinput> will open a save dialog in &kappname;’s VI mode."
msgstr ""
"Način VI se želi lepo integrirati s programom in odstopati od vedenja Vim, "
"kjer je to smiselno. Na primer, <userinput><command>:w</command></userinput> "
"bo odprl pogovorno okno za shranjevanje v načinu VI &kappname;."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the VI Input Mode for all new views, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kappname;...</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenu>Editing</guimenu><guimenuitem>VI Input Mode</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. On this tab you can set options for the VI Input "
"Mode and define and edit the key mapping in this mode. VI Input Mode can "
"also be toggled with the <guimenuitem>VI Input Mode</guimenuitem> setting in "
"the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu. (The default shortcut key is <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Meta;&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> - where &Meta; "
"usually is the <keysym>Windows</keysym> key)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti način vnosa VI za vse nove poglede, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kappname;...</guimenuitem> <guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vnos VI "
"Način</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na tem zavihku lahko nastavite možnosti za "
"način vnosa VI ter definirate in uredite preslikavo tipk v tem načinu. Način "
"vnosa VI lahko preklapljate tudi z nastavitvijo <guimenuitem>Način vnosa VI</"
"guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu>. (Privzeta bližnjična tipka "
"je <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Meta;&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> – "
"kjer je &Meta; običajno tipka <keysym>Windows</keysym>)."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many Vi Mode keyboard commands are case-sensitive, unlike most &kde; "
"keyboard shortcuts. That means that <userinput>y</userinput> and "
"<userinput>Y</userinput> are different commands. To enter the <userinput>y</"
"userinput> (yank) command, make sure <keysym>Caps Lock</keysym> is disabled "
"and press <keycap>Y</keycap>. To enter the <userinput>Y</userinput> (yank to "
"end of line) command, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Y</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Številni ukazi na tipkovnici načina Vi razlikujejo med velikimi in malimi "
"črkami, za razliko od večine &kde; bližnjice na tipkovnici. To pomeni, da "
"sta <userinput>y</userinput> in <userinput>Y</userinput> različna ukaza. Če "
"želite vnesti ukaz <userinput>y</userinput> (yank), se prepričajte, da je "
"<keysym>Caps Lock(Zaklepanje tipk)</keysym> onemogočen, in pritisnite "
"<keycap>Y</keycap>. Če želite vnesti ukaz <userinput>Y</userinput> "
"(potegnite na konec vrstice), <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Y</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This does not apply to commands that use the &Ctrl; key, which may be "
"entered regardless of <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> mode and without pressing "
"&Shift;. However, some commands require the use of a &Ctrl;-key combination "
"followed by another key which is case sensitive. For instance, to input "
"<quote><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<userinput>h</userinput></quote> (switch to split view right) make sure "
"<keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> is disabled, press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>, release, and then press <keycap>H</"
"keycap>."
msgstr ""
"To ne velja za ukaze, ki uporabljajo &Ctrl; tipko, ki jo lahko vnesete ne "
"glede na način <keycap>Caps Lock (Zaklepanje tipk)</keycap> in brez pritiska "
"&Shift;. Vendar nekateri ukazi zahtevajo uporabo kombinacije tipk &Ctrl;, ki "
"ji sledi druga tipka, ki razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. Na primer, "
"za vnos <quote><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></"
"keycombo>, <userinput>h</userinput></quote> (preklop na deljeni pogled "
"desno) poskrbite, da je <keycap>Caps Lock (Zaklepanje tipk)</keycap> "
"onemogočen, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></"
"keycombo>, spustite in nato pritisnite <keycap>H</keycap >."

#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incompatibilities with Vim"
msgstr "Nezdružljivosti z Vim"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are only a few features of &kappname;’s VI mode which are incompatible "
"with Vim (not counting things missing). They are listed below together with "
"the respective reasons."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja le nekaj funkcij načina VI &kappname;, ki niso združljive z Vimom "
"(če manjkajo stvari). Spodaj so navedeni skupaj z ustreznimi razlogi."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;: <userinput>U</userinput> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> is redo."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;: <userinput>U</userinput> in <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> se ponovi."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vim: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> is "
"normal redo, <keycap>U</keycap> is used to undo all latest changes on one "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Vim: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> je "
"običajno ponavljanje, <keycap>U</keycap> se uporablja za razveljavitev vseh "
"zadnjih sprememb v eni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The reason for having <keycap>U</keycap> act as redo in &kappname;’s VI mode "
"is that the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> by default is taken by &kappname;’s replace function (search and "
"replace). By default, the VI mode won’t override &kappname;’s shortcuts "
"(this can be configured in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kappname;...</guimenuitem> <guimenu>Editing</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Vi Input Mode</guimenuitem></menuchoice>), therefore a "
"redo-action needs to be available as a <quote>regular</quote> key press, "
"too. Besides, the behavior of the <userinput>U</userinput> command in Vim "
"does not map well to &kappname;’s internal undo system, so it would be non-"
"trivial to support anyway."
msgstr ""
"Razlog za to, da <keycap>U</keycap> deluje kot ponavljanje v načinu VI "
"&kappname; je, da je bližnjica <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> privzeto prevzame zamenjavna funkcija &kappname; (iskanje "
"in zamenjava). Privzeto način VI ne bo preglasil bližnjic &kappname; (to je "
"mogoče konfigurirati v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kappname;...</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vnosni način Vi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>), zato mora biti dejanje ponovitve na voljo tudi kot "
"<quote>običajen</quote> pritisk tipke. Poleg tega se vedenje ukaza "
"<userinput>U</userinput> v Vimu ne ujema dobro z notranjim sistemom za "
"razveljavitev &kappname;, tako da bi bilo vseeno netrivialno podpreti."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;: <userinput><command>print</command></userinput> shows the "
"<guilabel>Print</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;: <userinput><command>print</command></userinput> prikaže "
"pogovorno okno <guilabel>Natisni</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vim: <userinput><command>print</command></userinput> prints the lines of the "
"given range like its grandfather ed."
msgstr ""
"Vim: <userinput><command>print</command></userinput> natisne vrstice danega "
"obsega kot njegov stari ed."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Commands like <userinput><command>:print</command></userinput> are available "
"not only in the VI mode but for users using <quote>regular</quote> "
"&kappname;, too - therefore the <userinput><command>:print</command></"
"userinput> command opens the print dialog - following the principle of least "
"surprise instead of mimicking Vim’s behavior."
msgstr ""
"Ukazi, kot je <userinput><command>:print</command></userinput>, niso na "
"voljo le v načinu VI, ampak tudi za uporabnike, ki uporabljajo "
"<quote>običajni</quote> &kappname; - torej <userinput><command >:print</"
"command></userinput> ukaz odpre pogovorno okno za tiskanje - po načelu "
"najmanjšega presenečenja namesto posnemanja vedenja Vima."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kappname;: <userinput>Y</userinput> yanks to end of line."
msgstr "&kappname;: <userinput>Y</userinput> potegne na konec vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vim: <userinput>Y</userinput> yanks whole line, just like <userinput>y</"
"userinput><userinput>y</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Vim: <userinput>Y</userinput> potegne celotno vrstico, tako kot "
"<userinput>y</userinput><userinput>y</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"VI’s behavior for the <userinput>Y</userinput> command is in practice a bug. "
"For both change and delete commands, <userinput>c</userinput><userinput>c</"
"userinput>/ <userinput>d</userinput><userinput>d</userinput> will do its "
"action on the current line and <userinput>C</userinput>/<userinput>D</"
"userinput> will work from the cursor column to the end of the line. However, "
"both <userinput>y</userinput><userinput>y</userinput> and <userinput>Y</"
"userinput> yanks the current line. In &kappname;’s VI Mode <userinput>Y</"
"userinput> will yank to the end of the line. This is described as "
"<quote>more logical</quote> in the Vim <ulink url=\"http://vimdoc."
"sourceforge.net/htmldoc/change.html#Y\">documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vedenje VI za ukaz <userinput>Y</userinput> je v praksi napaka. Za ukaze za "
"spreminjanje in brisanje bo <userinput>c</userinput><userinput>c</"
"userinput>/ <userinput>d</userinput><userinput>d</userinput> opravil svoje "
"dejanje v trenutni vrstici in <userinput>C</userinput>/<userinput>D</"
"userinput> bo deloval od kazalnega stolpca do konca vrstice. Vendar tako "
"<userinput>y</userinput><userinput>y</userinput> kot <userinput>Y</"
"userinput> potegne trenutno vrstico. V načinu VI &kappname; bo <userinput>Y</"
"userinput> potegnil na konec vrstice. To je opisano kot <quote>bolj logično</"
"quote> v <ulink url=\"http://vimdoc.sourceforge.net/htmldoc/change.html#Y"
"\">dokumentaciji</ulink> za Vim."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;: <userinput>O</userinput> and <userinput>o</userinput> opens "
"[<replaceable>count</replaceable>] new lines and puts you in insert mode."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;: <userinput>O</userinput> in <userinput>o</userinput> odpre "
"[<replaceable>count</replaceable>] novih vrstic in vas postavi v način "
"vstavljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vim: <userinput>O</userinput> and <userinput>o</userinput> opens a new line "
"and inserts text [<replaceable>count</replaceable>] times when leaving "
"insert mode."
msgstr ""
"Vim: <userinput>O</userinput> in <userinput>o</userinput> odpre novo vrstico "
"in vstavi besedilo [<replaceable>count</replaceable>]-krat, ko zapusti način "
"vstavljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is mostly done as a consequence of witnessing many people being "
"confused by this behavior on a vim &irc; channel (#vim on Libera Chat)."
msgstr ""
"To se večinoma zgodi kot posledica opazovanja mnogih ljudi, ki jih to "
"vedenje zmede na vim &irc; kanal (#vim na Libera Chatu)."

#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Modes"
msgstr "Preklapljanje načinov"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Normal Mode</emphasis> permits you to enter commands to navigate "
"or edit a document, and is the default mode. You can return to it from any "
"other mode by pressing &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Običajni način</emphasis> vam omogoča vnos ukazov za krmarjenje "
"ali urejanje dokumenta in je privzeti način. Nanj se lahko vrnete iz "
"katerega koli drugega načina s pritiskom &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Visual Mode</emphasis> permits you to highlight text in a "
"document. Most Normal Mode commands are also valid in this mode. You can "
"enter it by pressing <userinput>v</userinput> to select characters or "
"<userinput>V</userinput> to select lines."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Vizualni način</emphasis> vam omogoča, da označite besedilo v "
"dokumentu. Večina ukazov običajnega načina je veljavnih tudi v tem načinu. "
"Vnesete ga lahko tako, da pritisnete <userinput>v</userinput> za izbiro "
"znakov ali <userinput>V</userinput> za izbiro vrstic."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Insert Mode</emphasis> permits you to edit the document directly. "
"You can enter it by pressing <userinput>i</userinput> or one of several "
"other commands listed below."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Način vstavljanja</emphasis> vam omogoča neposredno urejanje "
"dokumenta. Vnesete ga lahko tako, da pritisnete <userinput>i</userinput> ali "
"enega od več drugih ukazov, navedenih spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Command Mode</emphasis> invokes &kappname;'s command line, "
"permitting you to run many commands available in Vi implementations as well "
"as some specific to &kappname;. For more information on these commands, see "
"<xref linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\"/>. To use it, press "
"<keycap>:</keycap>, enter the command, and press &Enter;."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Ukazni način</emphasis> prikliče ukazno vrstico &kappname;, kar "
"vam omogoča zagon številnih ukazov, ki so na voljo v implementacijah Vi, kot "
"tudi nekaterih specifičnih za &kappname;. Za več informacij o teh ukazih "
"glejte <xref linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\"/>. Če ga želite "
"uporabiti, pritisnite <keycap>:</keycap>, vnesite ukaz in pritisnite &Enter;."

#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration with &kate; features"
msgstr "Integracija z &kate; Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Visual Mode is entered automatically when text is selected with the mouse. "
"It is also entered when using functions of &kate; that select text, such as "
"Select All (either from the menu or via <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>A</keycap> </keycombo>.)"
msgstr ""
"Vizualni način se vstopi samodejno, ko z miško izberete besedilo. Vnese se "
"tudi pri uporabi funkcij &kate; ki izberejo besedilo, na primer Izberi vse "
"(iz menija ali prek <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap> </"
"keycombo>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vi marks and <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">&kate; bookmarks</link> "
"are integrated. When a mark is created in Vi Mode, a corresponding &kate; "
"bookmark is created and appears in the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. "
"Conversely, when a &kate; bookmark is created, a corresponding Vi mark at "
"the 0 column is also created."
msgstr ""
"Vi oznake in <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">&kate; zaznamki</link> so "
"integrirani. Ko je oznaka ustvarjena v načinu Vi, se ustrezen &kate; "
"zaznamek je ustvarjen in prikazan v meniju <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu>. "
"Nasprotno, ko &kate; ustvari zaznamek, se ustvari tudi ustrezna oznaka Vi v "
"stolpcu 0."

#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported normal/visual mode commands"
msgstr "Podprti ukazi običajnega/vizualnega načina"

