#. Tag: title
#: vi.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Comma Text Object"
msgstr "Besedilni predmet vejica"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This object is missing in Vim. The comma text object makes it easy to modify "
"parameter lists in C-like languages and other comma separated lists. It is "
"basically the area between two commas or between a comma and a bracket. In "
"the line shown in the illustration, the three ranges this text object can "
"span are highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Ta predmet manjka v Vimu. Besedilni predmet z vejico olajša spreminjanje "
"seznamov parametrov v jezikih, podobnih C, in drugih seznamov, ločenih z "
"vejico. V bistvu je območje med dvema vejicama ali med vejico in oklepajem. "
"V vrstici, prikazani na sliki, so označeni trije obsegi, ki jih ta besedilni "
"predmet lahko zajema."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: vi.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>An example of Comma Text Object</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer besedilnega predmeta z vejico</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: vi.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>An example of Comma Text Object</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer besedilnega predmeta z vejico</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: vi.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comma text object ranges. If the cursor is over &eg; <replaceable>arg2</"
"replaceable>, pressing <userinput>ci</userinput>, (<quote>change inner "
"comma</quote>) would delete <replaceable>double arg2</replaceable> and place "
"the cursor between the two commas in insert mode. A very convenient way to "
"change a function's parameters."
msgstr ""
"Območja besedilnih predmetov vejice. Če je kazalec nad &eg; "
"<replaceable>arg2</replaceable>, s pritiskom <userinput>ci</userinput>, "
"(<quote>spremeni notranjo vejico</quote>) bi izbrisali <replaceable>dvojni "
"arg2</replaceable> in postavili kazalko med dve vejici v načinu vstavljanja. "
"Zelo priročen način za spreminjanje parametrov funkcije."

